com.bluegosling.collections.immutable

Interface ConsList<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of element in the list
    All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<E>, Iterable<E>, List<E>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractLinkedImmutableList, AbstractLinkedImmutableList.LinkedSubList, LinkedPersistentList

    public interface ConsList<E>
extends List<E>
    A list that is composed of cons cells. Implementations are generally simple, singly linked lists.
